subject: Olympic Games (2012)
Shooting (Sport)
Pregnancy and Childbirth
lead_paragraph: The air rifle competitor Nur Suryani Mohamed Taibi is set to join an exclusive club: just three other pregnant women are believed to have competed in the Olympics, all in the Winter Games.
